<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" lang="uz">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    <title>Tasdiqlash Kodingiz</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        /* Reset styles */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #0f2027;
            color: #ffffff;
            width: 100% !important;
            height: 100% !important;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        /* Main container */
        .email-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f2027 0%, #203a43 50%, #2c5364 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        
        /* Card container */
        .card {
            background-color: #1a1a2e;
            border: 2px solid #6495ed;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            margin: 0 auto;
            max-width: 400px;
        }
        
        /* Header styles */
        .header {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .title {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #6495ed;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(100, 149, 237, 0.3);
        }
        
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #a0a0a0;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        
        /* Code container */
        .code-container {
            background-color: #16213e;
            border: 2px solid #4169e1;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .code-label {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #a0a0a0;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        
        .verification-code {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #6495ed;
            letter-spacing: 8px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(100, 149, 237, 0.5);
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        
        /* Decorative elements */
        .code-container::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -1px;
            left: -1px;
            right: -1px;
            bottom: -1px;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #6495ed, #4169e1, #1e3c72);
            border-radius: 12px;
            z-index: -1;
        }
        
        /* Instructions */
        .instructions {
            background-color: #0f1419;
            border-left: 4px solid #6495ed;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }
        
        .instructions h3 {
            color: #6495ed;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .instructions p {
            color: #cccccc;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        
        /* Warning box */
        .warning {
            background-color: #2d1b16;
            border: 1px solid #ff6b35;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: left;
        }
        
        .warning-icon {
            color: #ff6b35;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 8px;
        }
  
        .warning-text {
            color: #ffcc99;
            font-size: 13px;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }
        
        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #333;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            color: #888;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        
        /* Responsive styles */
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                padding: 20px 10px;
            }
            
            .card {
                padding: 25px 20px;
            }
            
            .title {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            
            .verification-code {
                font-size: 30px;
                letter-spacing: 4px;
            }
            
            .instructions {
                padding: 15px;
            }
        }
        
        @media only screen and (max-width: 480px) {
            .verification-code {
                font-size: 24px;
                letter-spacing: 2px;
            }
        }
        
        /* Dark mode support */
        @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
            .card {
                background-color: #1a1a2e;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="card">
            <!-- Header -->
            <div class="header">
                <h1 class="title">üîê Tasdiqlash Kodi</h1>
                <p class="subtitle">Quyidagi kodni kiriting</p>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Verification Code -->
            <div class="code-container">
                <div class="code-label">Sizning kodingiz:</div>
                <div class="verification-code">{{code}}</div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Instructions -->
            <div class="instructions">
                <h3>üìã Qo'llanma:</h3>
                <p>
                    ‚Ä¢ Ushbu kodni tegishli maydonga kiriting<br>
                    ‚Ä¢ Kod 10 daqiqa davomida amal qiladi<br>
                    ‚Ä¢ Kodni hech kimga bermang
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Warning -->
            <div class="warning">
                <span class="warning-icon">‚ö†Ô∏è</span>
                <span class="warning-text">
                    <strong>Muhim:</strong> Agar siz bu amalni bajarmagansiz, ushbu emailni e'tiborsiz qoldiring va parolingizni o'zgartiring.
                </span>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Footer -->
            <div class="footer">
                <p>Bu avtomatik yuborilgan email hisoblanadi.</p>
                <p>¬© 2025 Sizning kompaniyangiz</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
